**TABLE OF CONTENTS**

1\. System Overview

The QUANTUM AI Content Factory is a multi-agent system that autonomously
discovers wellness trends, generates brand-compliant content, produces
AI-powered videos, and publishes them to social media platforms. The
system runs on Docker containers with n8n as the workflow orchestration
engine, PostgreSQL for data storage, Qdrant for vector search, and
Cloudflare Workers for the web dashboard.

1.1 Architecture Summary

  --------------- ------------------ ------------------------------------
  **Agent**       **Role**           **What It Does**

  ELECTRON-1      Trend Scout        Scans RSS feeds, Reddit, PubMed
                                     daily at 9AM Cairo. Scores 7-15
                                     wellness trends using Claude Haiku.
                                     Stores to trend_board.

  QUANTUM         Orchestrator       Reads top trends, checks for
                                     duplicates, creates 3 content
                                     briefs. Sends to Telegram for human
                                     approval.

  ELECTRON-2      Content Writer     Takes approved brief, retrieves
                                     brand rules from Qdrant, generates
                                     full content package via Claude
                                     Sonnet 4. Runs 3 QA gates (Haiku).

  ELECTRON-3      Video Producer     Routes to Kling (B2C cinematic) or
                                     HeyGen (B2B avatar). Produces video,
                                     stores in publish_logs.

  ELECTRON-4      Publisher (ORBIT)  Schedules and publishes videos to
                                     TikTok, Instagram, LinkedIn via
                                     platform APIs. 3 modes: Manual,
                                     Semi-Auto, Full Auto.
  --------------- ------------------ ------------------------------------

1.2 Daily Automated Flow

  ---------- ---------------------- ---------------------------------------
  **Time**   **Event**              **Details**

  9:00 AM    E1 Trend Scout fires   Cron trigger. Scans 6 sources (3 RSS, 2
                                    Reddit, 1 PubMed). Scores via Haiku.

  \~9:02 AM  QUANTUM auto-triggered Webhook from E1. Reads trend_board,
                                    checks dupes against content_briefs.

  \~9:04 AM  3 briefs arrive on     Each with Approve/Reject buttons. Human
             Telegram               reviews topic, module, platform.

  On Approve E2 generates content   Sonnet 4 creates hooks, script,
             (\~30s)                captions, CTA. 3 QA gates validate.

  On Approve Content preview on     Full content displayed with
             Telegram               Publish/Kill buttons.

  On Publish E3 produces video      Kling or HeyGen generates video.
             (\~2-5 min)            Preview sent to Telegram.

  On ORBIT   E4 publishes to        Manual mode: pick platforms via
             platforms              Telegram. Semi/Auto: scheduled or
                                    immediate.
  ---------- ---------------------- ---------------------------------------

