2\. Frontend: Dashboard (Mission Control)

The dashboard is a Cloudflare Worker at dashboard.corpfit.cloud. It
serves as the visual command center for the entire content factory. The
Worker proxies all /webhook/\* requests to n8n.corpfit.cloud,
eliminating CORS issues.

2.1 Dashboard Tabs

