3\. Frontend: Telegram Bot

The Telegram bot is the primary operator interface for content approval
and system monitoring. It uses polling (getUpdates) with no public URL
required.

3.1 Button Actions

  ------------ --------------- ------------------ -------------------------
  **Button**   **Stage**       **What Happens**   **Next Step**

  Approve      Brief review    Brief status →     Wait \~30s for content
                               approved. E2       preview
                               generates content  
                               automatically.     

  Reject       Brief review    Brief archived.    Done
                               Nothing generated. 

  Publish      Content review  Status →           Wait \~2-5 min for video
                               published. E3      
                               produces video.    

  Kill         Content review  Content archived.  Done
                               No video produced. 
  ------------ --------------- ------------------ -------------------------

