After E3 produces a video, 6 ORBIT buttons appear:

  --------------- --------------- ----------------------------------------
  **Button**      **Action**      **Effect**

  🎵 TikTok       Queue for       schedule_logs entry with status=queued,
                  TikTok only     platform=tiktok

  📸 Instagram    Queue for       schedule_logs entry for Instagram
                  Instagram only  

  💼 LinkedIn     Queue for       schedule_logs entry for LinkedIn
                  LinkedIn only   

  🚀 All          Queue for all 3 3 schedule_logs entries created
  Platforms                       simultaneously

