9.2 Two Funnels

  ------------ ---------------------- ------------------ --------------------
  **Funnel**   **Audience**           **Tone**           **CTA**

  B2C          Individual consumers   Fun, personal,     Download CorpFit
                                      relatable, casual  

  B2B          Corporate HR /         Professional,      Book a demo
               wellness managers      ROI-focused,       
                                      data-backed        
  ------------ ---------------------- ------------------ --------------------

9.3 Platform Tones

  -------------- -----------------------------------------------------------
  **Platform**   **Tone Requirements**

  TikTok         Fun, energetic, trendy, casual, Gen-Z friendly. 15-60s
                 vertical video. Emojis OK.

  Instagram      Inspiring, polished, aspirational, warm. Visual-first.
                 Moderate emojis.

  LinkedIn       Professional, data-driven, authoritative but approachable.
                 NO emojis in captions. NO slang. NO \'POV:\'.

  YouTube        Educational, friendly expert, in-depth, tutorial-style.
  -------------- -----------------------------------------------------------

9.4 Mandatory Brand Rules

-   **Brand name:** Always \"CorpFit\" (Circle of Resilient People).
    NEVER \"FunFit\" (old name).

-   **CTA rule:** Never use the word \"free\". CorpFit is a paid app
    with no free tier.

-   **B2C CTA:** Must include \"Download CorpFit\", \"Follow
    \@CorpFit\", or \"Save this\".

-   **B2B CTA:** Must include \"Book a demo\", \"Connect with CorpFit\",
    or \"Let\'s discuss\".

-   **Cross-funnel:** B2C cannot say \"Book a demo\". B2B cannot say
    \"Download\".

-   **Core mission:** \"Making health, losing weight, losing fat is
    FUN.\" Every piece must pass: Will people have fun doing this?

