12\. Troubleshooting

  ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------
  **Problem**            **Solution**

  Dashboard shows        Check if tunnel is running: open
  loading screen         n8n.corpfit.cloud. If down, restart cloudflared
                         from Task Scheduler.

  No briefs arriving on  Check E1 cron schedule in n8n. Verify RSS feeds
  Telegram               are still working. Run E1 manually via
                         dashboard.

  Content stuck in       Use /stale command in Telegram. Check if
  \'pending\'            Approval Handler v13 is active in n8n.

  QA gate blocking       Check error_logs for API failures. Gate
  everything             auto-passes on failure. If Haiku is down,
                         content flows through.

  \'429 Too Many         Anthropic rate limiting. Built-in retry logic (2
  Requests\' errors      attempts, 3s delay). If persistent, add delay
                         between briefs.

  Docker containers down Open Portainer (localhost:9000). Restart failed
                         containers. Check docker ps.

  Tunnel offline         Open Task Scheduler, find corpfit-tunnel task,
                         run it. Or: cloudflared tunnel run corpfit-n8n

  Dashboard buttons not  Hard refresh (Ctrl+Shift+R). Check browser
  working                console for JS errors. Verify worker deployed.

  Videos not generating  E3 needs Kling/HeyGen subscriptions. Check
                         publish_logs for error messages.

  ORBIT not publishing   Check system_config for PENDING_SETUP tokens.
                         Real API credentials needed.
  ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------

